Get ready for more mighty math missions with super-heroes, Milli, Geo, and Bot!
This season, join Team Umizoomi as they explore exciting places including Umi City
Skate Park, the Umi City Zoo, and their very own Headquarters with an Umi Workshop.
They'll also magically transform into space crusaders, Umi Ninjas, Umi cops, and
more. Listen carefully for the Umi Alarm and get ready to use your mighty math

out for Umi City's newest villains - the Troublemakers! Whether they're breaking
skateboards, letting penguins loose, or snatching lunches, it's up to you to chase
them down! Call on UmiCar for help. He's the coolest car around and this season,
the team throws him a big birthday party, and he'll also team up with his best
friend Shark Car at the Umi Grand Prix! Team Umizoomi, it's time for action!

Produced by Curious Pictures and Nickelodeon Productions.

with a problem. Max the Dragon lost his glasses and is flying around bumping
into everything in the kingdom! The UmiKnights must help the dragon!
